The '''Scohar Xenohealth Institute''' was a contagious-diseases research center located in [[Storinal]]'s capital city, [[Scohar]]. Its disease containment vault contained a [[Plasma bomb/Legends|plasma bomb]] large enough to incinerate the building and much of the surrounding area if its containment fields were breached. [[Wraith Squadron]] successfully infiltrated the Xenohealth Institute in order to obtain a sample of [[Bunkurd Sewer Disorder]] for use in a covert operation.<ref name="X-Wing: Wraith Squadron">''[[X-Wing: Wraith Squadron]]''</ref>

